  "remarks": "So-called ‘Head of the Donetsk People's Republic’ following the so-called elections of 11 November 2018. Former so-called Deputy Chairman of the ‘People's Council’ of the so-called ‘Donetsk People's Republic’. Former Speaker of the Donetsk People's Republic \"parliament\", the People's Council. Donetsk People's Republic's representative in the Contact Group for the Minsk talks; Listing: Listed on 19 Jun. 2014 (re-listed on 16 Jun. 2017, 10 June 2020 and 10 June 2023)",
